      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and it is in spectacular condition. Honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one\u2014it's always been garaged and I've kept up with every single service. It drives like a total dream and there isn't a scratch on it. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, you've found it! I'm happy to chat if you have any questions at all!",
