      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) features the coveted 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, delivering 385 hp with surgical precision. This example boasts a flawless PASM-equipped chassis and the Sport Chrono Package Plus for optimized throttle mapping and active engine mounts. Mechanically impeccable, the drivetrain exhibits zero seepage, and the 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast, rev-matched downshifts. Every bushing, seal, and synchro remains tight, reflecting its pampered history and meticulous preventative maintenance. Finished with a ceramic-coated exterior and a pristine, smoke-free cabin, this is a turn-key specimen for the discerning enthusiast seeking the pinnacle of hydraulic-steering feedback and analog engagement.",
